SUMMARY:Easter Brunch at Rusty Pelican
LOCATION:2425 N Rocky Point Dr Tampa \, FL 33607 United States
DESCRIPTION:Hop over to Rusty Pelican Tampa for a special three-course Eas
 ter brunch featuring family-style shareable starters and fan-favorite raw 
 bar filled with fresh coastal delicacies like Chilled Oysters and ancho ch
 ili cocktail sauce\, Fresh Salmon Poke\, or upgrade and taste it all with 
 our signature Hot Seafood Tower. Savor elevated takes on classic brunch di
 shes for your main course\, like Hot Honey Fried Chicken Belgian Waffle wi
 th maple syrup and whipped butter\, and Lobster Benedict with poached eggs
 \, classic hollandaise\, and buttery Atlantic lobster. Last but not least\
 , finish the meal with indulgent desserts made to be shared\, like Limonce
 llo Tiramisu\, Pineapple Upside-Down Cake\, and Strawberry Shortbread. Ele
 vate your brunch experience with mix-and-match bottomless mimosas. Try uni
 que bubbly flavors like watermelon and lime\, cucumber and mint\, mango an
 d Tajin\, and the classic orange. Easter Brunch at Rusty Pelican is 105 fo
 r adults and 35 for children. Bottomless mimosas can be added for 30 per p
 erson. Reservations are highly encouraged and can be made here (https:bit.
 lyeaster_at_rpt). Rusty Pelican Tampa will also be open for dinner service
 . \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187396
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/187396
END:VEVENT
