 lp you shake off stiffness\, open tight muscles\, and invite in lighter\, 
 easier movementjust like the season itself. No equipment needed\, just a f
 ew minutes to pause\, unwind\, and spring into motion. Hula Hoop Fun! Join
  a quick hula hoop contest right after the stretch breakwinner gets a spec
 ial prize at each location! No registration needed  just show up! Bonus Pe
 rks Prizes for all participants (while supplies last) Counts toward Optum 
